                            <comment id="272063" author="emoly.liu" created="Fri, 5 Jun 2020 13:04:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I looked into the code and found &quot;-D&quot; options was removed by the patch at &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/32977&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/32977&lt;/a&gt; and re-added by the patch at &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/20552&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/20552&lt;/a&gt; , but the related value LFS_OPT_DIRECTIO is never used.&lt;br/&gt;
